# Git workflow (gustavtraff/oden)

This repository is a **personal fork**, not the upstream project.

## Never do unless the user explicitly asks

- Create pull requests (on this fork or anywhere else)
- Push to upstream (`NicklasAndersson/oden`)
- Open or suggest PRs against upstream
- Propose "feature branch → PR → merge" as the default workflow

## Default workflow

- Work on `main` or a local branch
- Commit only when the user explicitly requests a commit
- Push to `origin` (`gustavtraff/oden`) only when the user explicitly requests a push
- Pull latest `main` from `origin` before starting new work
